description: "Take Sandbox with you wherever you go. Place Infinite Item Sources, Liquid Sources, and Power Sources on any map or game mode—no Sandbox mode required. Perfect for testing, creative builds, or completely abandoning the idea of resource management.\n\nWhat could possibly go wrong?\nNo..? Okay this is legal then :)\n\n⚠ Warning: using this mod may cause you to lose the intended game experience due to having access to unlimited resources."
